Package mystars.entities

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Index.IndexCallback
    Callback function to be executed when an event happens.
    IStorage
    This Istorage interface contains the abstract methods for storing and retrieving serializable objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Course
    This class performs all the functions required for courseController.
    Entity
    This class provides helper functions for persistance of child classes.
    FileStorage
    This class stores serializable data to a flat file on disk
    Index
    This index class manages creation of lessons within an index and the relationship between student and index.
    Lesson
    This class represents a Lesson.
    Registration
    This class represents one index added to a timetable and tracks the current status of this relationship.
    Student
    This student class inherits from the user class, and is responsible for the creation of a new student object.
    Timetable
    This class implements the student's timetable.
    User
    This user class serves as the superclass for 'admin' and 'student'.
  • Enum Summary

    The events which can be observed on this class.

    Possible states of this Registration.
